data.description: Dollhouse of the neighborhood! Introducing a stunning colonial-inspired home in the heart of Placerville. With its charming exterior and interior elements, this property exudes a timeless style. Inside, you'll find a well-designed floor plan featuring 3 beds & 2 full bathrooms, and a living room with a cozy fireplace. Original oak wood flooring graces most of the home, adding character and warmth. The kitchen offers a comfortable design and seamlessly connects to the adjoining dining area for effortless entertainment. Step through the back mud room to discover a relaxing deck and fully fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Additional highlights include; New HVAC, Newer roof, a front covered porch, garage, and ample parking. Best of all, this home is conveniently located within a short walking distance to downtown Placerville's vibrant restaurants, shops & events. This is more than just a home, it's a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and charm. Make it yours today!
